// Build personalized email sequence
const { leadId, email, firstName, tradeType, painPoints, outreachAngle } = $input.item.json;

const painStr = painPoints?.[0] ?? 'running your business manually';
const trade = tradeType ?? 'contractor';

const sequence = [
  {
    day: 0,
    subject: `Quick question, ${firstName}`,
    body: `Hey ${firstName},

I came across your work and noticed you're running a ${trade} business.

Quick question: are you still manually handling ${painStr}?

Most ${trade}s I talk to are losing $2-3k/month in unbilled jobs and missed follow-ups. We built an AI crew to fix that.

Would a quick 5-minute look make sense?

— The TitanCrew Team
https://app.titancrew.ai/demo?lead=${leadId}`
  },
  {
    day: 2,
    subject: `${trade} business tip (saves ~8 hrs/week)`,
    body: `Hey ${firstName},

Before I follow up on my last message — wanted to share something useful.

Most ${trade} businesses lose 8+ hours/week to: scheduling back-and-forth, chasing unpaid invoices, remembering to follow up with leads.

TitanCrew's AI crew handles all 3 automatically. Takes 10 minutes to set up.

Still think this could be useful for you: https://app.titancrew.ai/demo?lead=${leadId}

— The TitanCrew Team`
  },
  {
    day: 4,
    subject: `${firstName}, did this land in spam?`,
    body: `Hey ${firstName},

Just checking — I've sent a couple notes and want to make sure I'm not being annoying.

If you're not interested in automating your ${trade} business, just reply NO and I'll never bother you again.

But if the timing is right — here's a 30-second demo I made for your trade:
https://app.titancrew.ai/demo?lead=${leadId}&trade=${tradeType}

— TitanCrew`
  },
  {
    day: 7,
    subject: `What other ${trade}s are saying...`,
    body: `Hey ${firstName},

Last thing I'll share:

"My TitanCrew booked 4 jobs while I was on a job site. I didn't touch my phone once." — Marcus, HVAC contractor in Phoenix

That's the goal — a business that runs itself when you're in the field.

If you ever want to see what this looks like for your setup:
https://app.titancrew.ai/demo?lead=${leadId}

— TitanCrew`
  },
  {
    day: 10,
    subject: `Last one from me, ${firstName}`,
    body: `Hey ${firstName},

This is my last note — I don't want to clutter your inbox.

If TitanCrew isn't the right fit right now, no worries. Running a ${trade} business is hard and timing matters.

If you ever want to check it out in the future:
https://app.titancrew.ai

Wishing you a busy season,
— The TitanCrew Team`
  }
];

return [{ json: { leadId, email, firstName, sequence } }];
